<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Há»— trá»£ khÃ¡ch hÃ ng - Quáº£n trá»‹</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <style>
